metadata.name: KING'S GALA # 1
metadata.description: King's Gala is the a randomly generated of collection of King Incooom's favorite outfits spanning the decades of his reign.  These randomly generated profile pictures are a hat tip to the PFP's that came before us.  As we enter the TAKEOVER EPOCH at INCOOOM, we must always remember where we came from.  Enjoy the KING in all his glory as possessing HIS HIGHNESS brings nobility wherever you step foot in the METAVERSE.
